Oh right,

39
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:42,870
I've got a gift for you too.

40
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,470
Nuo, you...

41
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:50,870
Because of one tiny mistake,

42
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:52,150
you beat me to the punch.

43
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,240
I actually prepared

44
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,750
