54
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:38,450
♪I miss you, miss you, miss you♪

55
00:03:38,450 --> 00:03:43,210
♪So much in the darkest night♪

56
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:44,850
♪I cannot♪

57
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:49,240
♪Help giving you my heart♪

58
00:03:49,490 --> 00:03:51,230
♪My body♪

59
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,010
♪My everything♪

60
00:03:53,150 --> 00:03:57,630
♪I love you 'til the moon sinks♪

61
00:03:57,970 --> 00:04:01,330
♪And the stars fall from sight♪

62
00:04:01,460 --> 00:04:04,610
♪You are the only love♪

63
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:09,700
♪Of my life♪

64
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,240
Do you love me?

65
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,870
What do you think?

66
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,800
I want to hear it from your mouth.

67
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:21,920
I love you.

68
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,680
I love you too.

69
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:27,600
