75
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,310
She proposed to me yesterday.

76
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,160
Who is it?

77
00:07:07,270 --> 00:07:07,920
She's giving me the look right now.

78
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,560
Stop making stuff up!

79
00:07:10,040 --> 00:07:11,270
No work today.

80
00:07:11,310 --> 00:07:12,120
Maybe tomorrow!

81
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,390
You're so annoying!

82
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:14,390
