83
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:15,750
Relax.

84
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,070
That was just the alarm.

85
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,390
They know we're together.

86
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,120
Who would dare interrupt us?

87
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,800
You're so annoying!

88
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,430
So I wasn't wrong, was I?

89
00:07:46,070 --> 00:07:47,560
[Uncle Xu]
Just now, who said,

90
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,310
"They know we're together.

91
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,750
Who would dare interrupt us?"

92
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,040
It's your dad.

93
00:08:01,460 --> 00:08:04,180
[Nuo: He becomes my private property.]

94
00:08:04,180 --> 00:08:07,260
[Jiahe: She said "I do."]

95
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,190
Jiahe,

96
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:15,430
last time you two pretended to be a couple.

97
00:08:15,430 --> 00:08:17,750
It was to protect Xu Nuo's reputation.

98
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,870
What's going on

99
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:19,950
between you two this time?

100
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,390
Uncle Xu,

101
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:22,360
we're both adults.

102
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,430
We'll take full responsibility

103
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,190
for our relationship.

104
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,480
What relationship?

105
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,190
Are you out of your mind?

106
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:30,310
You two are like siblings!

107
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,830
She's being reckless,

108
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,440
and you're going along with it?

109
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,320
But we

110
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,840
are not related by blood.

111
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,960
And Xu Nuo and I truly love each other.

112
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:38,720
Enough!

113
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,790
Stop right there.

114
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,120
Don't say another word.

115
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,670
If you two keep this up,

116
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,480
how am I

117
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:45,480
supposed to face anyone?

118
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:46,720
Jiahe,

119
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:47,750
you know

120
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,000
what Xu Nuo's temper is like.

121
00:08:49,030 --> 00:08:50,200
She may seem fine now,

122
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:51,320
but if you two

123
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,720
ever get into a serious fight,

124
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:54,360
it'll be earth-shattering!

125
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,440
I really don't want Yuanfei Group

126
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:57,440
to collapse because of internal conflict one day!

127
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,360
Uncle Xu,

128
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,630
don't worry about that.

129
00:09:03,550 --> 00:09:04,910
No matter what happens,

130
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:06,790
I'll always yield to Xu Nuo.

131
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,750
If one day

132
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,720
we truly can't get along,

133
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,120
I'll leave Yuanfei Group.

134
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:18,000
You're going to drive me mad.

135
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:19,000
I know no matter what I say now,

136
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,120
neither of you will listen.

137
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:23,360
Fine, do whatever you want.

138
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:25,440
You're leaving next week anyway.

139
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:26,750
Let's see

140
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:28,000
how long this relationship of yours will last.

141
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,150
Su Rong.

142
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,270
How long are you going to avoid me?

143
00:09:54,910 --> 00:09:55,910
What's going on?

144
00:09:58,150 --> 00:09:59,120
Why do you act like

145
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,240
I'm your mortal enemy whenever you see me?

146
00:10:02,150 --> 00:10:03,870
Even if we're divorced,

147
00:10:04,870 --> 00:10:06,390
when it comes to the kids,

148
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,240
can't we

149
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:08,790
have a calm conversation?

150
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,440
The kids?

151
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:14,080
You hit Xu Nuo

152
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,750
because of Bai Xia.

153
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:15,910
I haven't

154
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:17,390
even settled that score with you.

155
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,270
Oh...

156
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,600
I don't know what came over me back then.

157
00:10:19,630 --> 00:10:20,240
I...

158
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:21,550
I completely lost my temper.

159
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:23,120
It was a slip of the hand.

160
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:26,270
Oh, by the way...

161
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:29,080
Shen Jiahe and Xu Nuo are getting married.

162
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,360
Did you know?

163
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:31,600
Of course I knew.

164
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,720
They're not blood-related,

165
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,750
so why are you so bothered?

166
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:38,080
Shen Jiahe publicly says

167
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,440
he's our adopted son.

168
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,150
They may not be siblings by blood,

169
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:42,390
but they grew up like siblings!

170
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:43,840
I've tried talking to them,

171
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,150
but they won't listen.

172
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:46,960
Why don't you talk to them instead?

173
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:47,630
Please?

174
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,270
This wedding can't happen!

175
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:54,440
Xu Mingli,

176
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:57,750
you're fighting this so hard.

177
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,510
Are you hiding something

178
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:01,440
from me?

179
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:05,510
Me?

180
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:09,750
What could I possibly be hiding?

181
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:10,960
I'm just worried

182
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,030
people will talk about our family.

183
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,200
Fine.

184
00:11:18,270 --> 00:11:20,240
Then here's where I stand.

185
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:23,390
Not only will I not stop them,

186
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,150
but I'm going to that wedding

187
00:11:25,150 --> 00:11:26,630
to witness their happiness myself.

188
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,670
If you dare ruin it,

189
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,480
I'll be the first to come after you.

190
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,320
Calm down for a second.

191
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:36,960
Just listen.

192
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,390
You can't let your grudge against me

193
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,670
cloud your judgment

194
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,360
and ruin the kids' future

195
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,390
and happiness!

196
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:44,150
Don't flatter yourself!

197
00:11:44,270 --> 00:11:45,910
Who said I'm doing this to spite you?

198
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:46,840
Get out of the way!

199
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:47,720
Those two

200
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,480
really can't be together!

201
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,150
Step aside!

202
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,390
Mom,

203
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,750
Nuo and I

204
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:07,910
grew up together.

205
00:12:08,390 --> 00:12:10,270
We know each other well and trust each other.

206
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,870
So we've decided

207
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,720
to get married soon.

208
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:15,630
Get married?

209
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,120
No!

210
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,320
No marriage!

211
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,480
Don't get married!

212
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,240
No way!

213
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:22,910
Mom.

214
00:12:23,630 --> 00:12:23,960
It can't happen!

215
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,550
Mom...

216
00:12:24,550 --> 00:12:24,670
Aunt Fen.

217
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:25,480
- What's wrong, Mom? - Aunt Fen.

218
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,320
No!

219
00:12:26,390 --> 00:12:26,670
Aunt Fen.

220
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:27,550
- Okay. - No!

221
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:28,670
- It's alright. - No wedding!

222
00:12:28,670 --> 00:12:29,240
It can't happen!

223
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:29,840
It's okay.

224
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,870
No wedding.

225
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:31,200
No marriage!

226
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:32,030
It's alright, Mom.

227
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:33,030
It's okay.

228
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:33,550
No wedding!

229
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,840
No wedding!

230
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,720
It's over now,

231
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,270
Mom.

232
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,440
That didn't scare you too much, right?

233
00:12:54,790 --> 00:12:55,870
I'll head back by myself.

234
00:12:55,870 --> 00:12:56,790
You can stay and take care of Aunt Fen.

235
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:58,480
Ao Zhe's car should be here soon.

236
00:13:01,910 --> 00:13:03,600
Has she ever been like this before?

237
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,550
She's had emotional moments,

238
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,550
but never this bad.

239
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:14,200
Just now,

240
00:13:15,030 --> 00:13:16,200
it really seemed

241
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:17,390
like she didn't want us to get married.

242
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:20,670
Don't overthink it.

243
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,080
With Aunt Fen like this,

244
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:26,510
can you really feel at ease going to Singapore?

245
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:28,960
I'll come back to visit you two often.

246
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:30,670
Besides,

247
00:13:30,870 --> 00:13:32,120
you'll still be here, won't you?

248
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:37,840
Jiahe,

249
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,150
in the past,

250
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:42,840
I said a lot of things that hurt you

251
00:13:43,390 --> 00:13:44,150
and did things

252
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,550
that upset you.

253
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,000
I was hoping

254
00:13:47,030 --> 00:13:48,320
now that we're finally together,

255
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:50,240
I could make it up to you.

256
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,480
But now, you're being transferred again.

257
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,910
Who knows how long till we meet again?

258
00:13:58,030 --> 00:14:00,080
I'm a little worried...

259
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:03,630
Worried about what?

260
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:08,790
You were overseas for so many years,

261
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,720
but my feelings for you

262
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,600
never changed.

263
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:12,790
What are you worried about?

264
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:19,600
Don't worry.

265
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,440
I'll come back as soon as I can.

266
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,600
I believe you.

267
00:14:28,910 --> 00:14:30,240
Then you have to promise me,

268
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:32,080
that no matter how many uncertainties

269
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:33,120
we face in the future,

270
00:14:33,550 --> 00:14:34,910
we'll always be honest with each other.

271
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:36,360
Alright.

272
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:37,790
I promise.

273
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:46,480
No need to worry.

274
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:03,220
[Six months later]

275
00:15:04,940 --> 00:15:09,860
[Xiamei Skincare Club]

276
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:11,320
Unbelievable!

277
00:15:12,870 --> 00:15:14,320
Blank Capital is suing us?

278
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,440
Even if they're the investor,

279
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:16,550
they can't just go back on their word!

280
00:15:17,080 --> 00:15:17,870
What's their excuse?

281
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,630
They're accusing us

282
00:15:20,600 --> 00:15:21,670
of commercial fraud.

283
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:23,360
And they somehow knew

284
00:15:23,390 --> 00:15:24,030
we pulled the funds

285
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:25,480
from somewhere else.

286
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:28,790
It must've been last month's

287
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:30,360
huge spending that made them suspicious.

288
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:33,790
It's all Xu Mingli's fault!

289
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,120
He rushed to pull the money out.

290
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,480
We already poured a ton

291
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,440
into those downtown storefronts

292
00:15:39,630 --> 00:15:41,080
